snippet.title: Escape From Russia: Mobilization trailer
snippet.description:
Here is Steam page link for the game:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2251380/Escape_From_Russia_Mobilization/
If you like the game and want support us please add game to wishlist and follow for news! You can also send this video or steam page to your friend!
We also have steam group:
https://steamcommunity.com/groups/GosDev
And curator group:
https://store.steampowered.com/curator/39326232/
Where we will make some giveaways for our games!
